      <title>大选风险消退，美国股市命运取决于企业盈利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/fate-of-us-stocks-hinges-on-earnings-as-election-risk-clears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普在美国总统大选获胜后投资者的注意力重新转向经济增长，企业盈利将成为美国股市的最大推动力之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/fate-of-us-stocks-hinges-on-earnings-as-election-risk-clears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 10:16:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
